<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Ptolemais Hormou</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Παψαῦς Ἀσκλᾶτι τῶι ἀδελφῷ πολλὰ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>ἀσπάζομαί σε καὶ ὅλον τὸν οἶκόν σου. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἤδη δεύτερόν σοι ἐπιστόλιον γράφω περὶ 

    <lb n="4"/>τοῦ νεκροῦ τοῦ ἀπὸ Οὐισέμτου στρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>τιώτου 

    <lb n="5"/>τοῦ λεγιωναρίου οὗ <choice><corr>ἐνήνοχαν</corr><sic>ενηνεχαν</sic></choice> σοι οἱ ἀπὸ 

    <lb n="6"/>Τμουναχῆ καὶ οἱ ἀπὸ Φεβῖχις Κου<hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>τει-

    <lb n="7"/>λεῖς καὶ ὁ μετ᾽ αὐτοῦ, ὃν ἔδωκαν τῷ <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ἱῷ σου. 

    <lb n="8"/>καὶ <choice><corr>σημεῖον</corr><sic>σημιον</sic></choice>, ὅτι εἰς τὸν νῶτον αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="9"/>ῥάβδον <supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">  </supplied> καὶ ἐμβεβλημένοι εἰσὶν αὐτὸν ἐπὶ 

    <lb n="10"/>τὴν ὄνον σου καὶ τοῦ <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ἱοῦ  σου καὶ καθέστα-

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>καν</corr><sic>κατεστακαν</sic></choice> αὐτὸν ἔσω παρὰ σὸν μετὰ τοῦ <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ἱοῦ 

    <lb n="12"/>σου. τὰ νῦν ταῦτα πάντα γράφω σοι περὶ 

    <lb n="13"/>αὐτοῦ <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να αὐτὸν καταστήσητε εἰς τὴν 

    <lb n="14"/>κώμην αὐτοῦ. <choice><corr>ἐπεὶ</corr><sic>επι</sic></choice> δὲ <hi rend="diaeresis">ὕ</hi>βριν προσέλαβα 

    <lb n="15"/>ὧδε μεγάλην καὶ ἐγγὺς ἐπὶ τὸν ἡγεμό-

    <lb n="16"/>να με εἵλκυσαν, οὐ καθ᾽ ὑμᾶς ὃ ἐποιήσατέ 

    <lb n="17"/>μοι. ἄλλο <choice><corr>σημεῖόν</corr><sic>σημιον</sic></choice> σοι γράφω περὶ αὐτοῦ, 

    <lb n="18"/><choice><corr>ὅτι</corr><sic>οτε</sic></choice> ἡ γυνή σου ἐξελθοῦσα ἠγόρακε ὀβο-

    <lb n="19"/>λῶν τεσσάρων <num value="4"/> ἀρτύματα τῷ ναυτικῷ 

    <lb n="20"/>τῷ ἀπὸ Τμουναχῆ ἐπικαλουμένῳ Κου<hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>-

    <lb n="21"/>τειλεῖ. οὐ καλῶς μοι <choice><corr>ἐχρήσασθε</corr><sic>εχρησαστε</sic></choice> μὴ κα-

    <lb n="22"/>ταστήσαντες αὐτὸν εἰς τὸν τόπον αὐ-

    <lb n="23"/>τοῦ. ἀσπάζομαί σε καὶ τὸν <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ἱόν σου καὶ ὅλον 

    <lb n="24"/>τὸν οἶκόν σου. ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὐχομαι. Φα<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρμοῦθι</unclear> <num value="19">ιθ</num>. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="25"/>ἀπόδος <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> Κε<gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/>      <g type="x"/>     Ἀσκλᾶτι ἀπὸ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Πα</supplied>-

    <lb n="26"/>ψαῦτος <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">φίλ</unclear>ου. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.8847" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.8847" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="101" notAfter="200">II</date></p></div><div n="meta.8847" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Tag: 14. Apr.</p></div><div n="meta.8847" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.8847" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Petaus</title><biblScope type="numbers">28</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">8847</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0185</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">28</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0185;;28" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.8847" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">277</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.8847" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Tafel XI</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.8847" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="low" full="yes">Herakleopolites</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.8847" type="figure" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete">